Package: shiny.ollama
Version: 0.1.0
Title: 'Shiny' Interface for 'Ollama'
Description: A web application framework that enables interaction with 'Ollama' large 
    language models through 'Shiny'. Provides functions for managing local language 
    models, generating text responses, and conducting chat-based interactions. Features 
    include model loading and unloading, prompt construction, response streaming, and 
    chat history management. Simplifies the integration of local AI capabilities into 
    'Shiny' applications without requiring cloud services or API keys.
